snippet.title: Diana and Roma Visit the Zoo and Learn about Animals
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma visit the zoo in the city of Kiev, Ukraine. In this zoo you can pet the animals and even feed them. Children learn about different types of animals, about their characteristics and habits. Diana and Roma experienced positive emotions while communicating with these cute animals and decided to share with you.
Thanks for watching!
